MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 784

DECLARING AS CIVIL RESERVATION FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE BARRA ELEMENTARY AND NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOLS, CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARRA, DIPOLOG CITY, PROVINCE OF ZAMBOANGA DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO.

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO, President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby declare as civil reservation for school site purposes of the Barra Elementary and High Schools under the administration of the Department of Education, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Barra, Dipolog City, Province of Zamboanga del Norte, Island of Mindanao, subject to private rights, if any there be, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

LOT 1, SGS-09-000639

A PARCEL OF LAND, (Lot 1, Sgs-09-000639, being a portion of Lot 914, Cad-85, situated in Barra, Dipolog City, Province of Zamboanga del Norte, Island of Mindanao.

Bounded on the SW., along line 1-2 by Lot No. 19; along line 2-3 by Lot No. 18; along line 3-4 by Lot No. 17, all of Cad-85; along line 4-5 by Quezon Avenue; along line 5-6 by Lot No. 16; along line 6-7 by Lot No. 15 along line 7-8 by Lot No. 14, all of Cad-85; on the NW., along lines 8-9-10 by Burgos Street (existing concrete road); on the NE., along line 10-11 by Lot No. 7, Sgs-4126; and on the SE., along line 11-1 by Balintawak Street (Extension), being a portion of Lot No. 914, Cad-85, Dipolog Cadastre.

Beginning at point marked “1” on plan being N. 56 deg. 57′ E., 535.77 meters from BLLM No. 1, Cad 85, Dipolog Cadastre, thence:

17.19 m. to point 2;

23.46 m. to point 3;

18.36 m. to point 4;

10.12 m. to point 5;

17.89 m. to point 6;

24.07 m. to point 7;

34.24 m. to point 8;

134.49 m. to point 9;

40.88 m. to point 10;

99.17 m. to point 11;

161.35 m. to point of

Beginning, containing an area of TWENTY ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED NINETY TWO (21,992) square meters, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows: Points 9 and 10 by GS; Points 11 by Old PS Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 50 cms. and the rest by Old BL Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cms. Bearings Grid; Date of Survey April 26-27, 2001 and was approved on December 3, 2003.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 7th day of February, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

